snippet.title: Hamenos - March 2024
snippet.description:
Hi everyone! I'm excited to share the latest gameplay from Hamenos. 
A big thank you to everyone who participated in the event yesterday!

Hamenos is an ambitious project developed by a solo developer. 
If you're interested in supporting my work, please join our Discord server, play the game, and share your feedback. 
Thank you!

PLAY NOW: https://hamenos.com/play.html
Discord: https://discord.gg/AvWNBF4nX8

Song: JPB - Defeat The Night (feat. Ashley Apollodor) [NCS Release]
Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds
Free Download/Stream: http://ncs.io/defeat
Watch: http://youtu.be/A_AtqKMqPUE
